---

**Key principles**

- Step Functions executions are fully ephemeral
- Scaling controller is the only thing managing concurrency
- Executions self report completion via SignalComplete
- Controller cleanup is safety net for stuck or orphaned executions only
- DestroyDevbox → SignalComplete always runs regardless of outcome
- CI result pushed via EventBridge, never polled
- All inference steps hard bounded, no open ended loops
- EscalateToHuman preserves partial work
- DeadLetterEscalate handles infrastructure failures
